# Privacy Policy

**Effective Date:** July 10, 2025  
**App Name:** ApiaryAI  
**Developer:** Daniel Najda Pty Ltd  
**Contact:** danielnajda@danielnajda.com

This Privacy Policy describes how ApiaryAI ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our mobile application.

---

## 1. Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information:

- **Location Data:** To record GPS coordinates of apiary sites and hive placements.
- **Media Access:** Photos and audio recordings taken through the app.
- **Account Information:** Email, username, or login credentials used to access the app.
- **Analytics:** We collect anonymized usage data via Google Analytics to improve the app.
- **Device Info:** Basic metadata like device type, OS version, and crash reports.

---

## 2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

- Provide access to app features
- Save and sync your inspection data
- Track and manage apiary site locations
- Process purchases through RevenueCat
- Analyze and improve app performance

---

## 3. Data Sharing

We do **not sell** or rent your personal data.

We only share necessary data with trusted third-party tools used to operate the app:

- **Firebase** (data storage and login)
- **RevenueCat** (purchase validation)
- **Google Analytics** (anonymous usage data)

These services have their own privacy policies and comply with industry-standard data security.

---

## 4. Data Storage & Security

All inspection data and login credentials are stored securely using Firebase.  
We use encrypted communication to protect data in transit.

However, we cannot guarantee absolute security. You are responsible for exporting your inspection data regularly in case of app deletion or device loss.

---

## 5. Your Rights

You have the right to:

- Request a copy of your data
- Delete your account and associated content
- Contact us with privacy concerns or corrections

Reach out to us any time at: **danielnajda@danielnajda.com**

---

## 6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

ApiaryAI is not specifically targeted at children under the age of 16, but they are not restricted from using it.

We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under 16 years of age. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected personal data from a child, we will delete that information promptly.

Parents or guardians may contact us at danielnajda@danielnajda.com to review or delete data associated with a minor's use of the app.

---

## 7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy from time to time. When we do, we will revise the "Effective Date" at the top.

You are encouraged to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your data.

---

